query:
INSERT INTO merges (id, task_attempt_id, merge_commit) 
               VALUES ($1, $2, $3)
               RETURNING 
                   id as "id!: Uuid",
                   task_attempt_id as "task_attempt_id!: Uuid",
                   merge_commit as "merge_commit!",
                   merged_at as "merged_at!: DateTime<Utc>"
